info.description:
=====
MagicStat
=====

MagicStat is a statistical data analytics platform for people with 
little knowledge and experience of performing certain statistical models.


Quick start
-----------

1. Add "MagicStat" to your INSTALLED_APPS setting like this::

    INSTALLED_APPS = [
        ...
        'MagicStat',
    ]

2. Include the polls URLconf in your project urls.py like this::

    path('magicstat/', include('MagicStat.urls')),
	
3. Include the url and directory name of static files in the settings.py file.

	STATIC_URL = '/static/'

4. Visit http://127.0.0.1:8000/magicstat/ to run the MagicStat application.
